Class GameModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.prasannjeet.battleship.model.GameModel

  • public class GameModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Prasannjeet Description: A simple POJO class that represents the GameInstance model in a simpler format that can be sent to the client. This is used to draw the boards in the client side.
